<br>
I've said a few times recently that I think the calendar would work best if it was used solely for Hate, Fear, Growth, Sky, and other zones that require respectable time and/or plat investments to get to and have considerable respawn times.<br>
<br>
If you agree with me, no need to post.  I only need to hear why not to change the calendar to very explicitly state that it is meant for these specific places.<br>
Tell me why Vox and Nagafen (and all the other dragons) should still be put on the calendar.<br>
Tell me why Orc2 is just as expensive to get to as Sky.<br>
<br>
I'll leave this up probably for two weeks.  If we don't get any resistance to this change I'll be modifying the text on the calendar and front page as well as removing all calendar posts that deal with dragons, epic mobs (not including ones in a plane), Phinny, Orc2, etc.<br>
<br>
Please *explain* how the calendar makes it *easier* compared to the message board.<br>
<br>
The calendar is only there to make it easier to work together.  A &quot;reservation&quot; on the calendar is no different than a &quot;reservation&quot; on the message boards, just alot easier to read and schedule when you've got 12 guilds consisting of 4521 players all wanting to get into the same 3 planes.  I'm just getting the feeling that all the dragon reserving and such is more difficult to follow than more of a list style thing in the forums. <p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#000000"><tr><td align="center" colspan="2"><img src="http://everquest.estoncom.com/noj/images/bishsign1.gif" border="0" alt="Get yer foul tallard mouse cursor OFF OF ME!"></td><td rowspan="2" align="center"><font color="#FFFFDD" size="1" face="tempus sans itc">and...</font><br><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=44611"><font color="#29FF29" face="tempus sans itc" size="3">Kraket</font></a><br><br><font color="#8888FF" face="tempus sans itc" size="2">The<br>narcoleptic <br>lizard</font></td></tr><tr><td align="center" colspan="2"><a href="http://pub30.ezboard.com/bnuggetsofjustice"><font color="#FF0042" face="tempus sans itc" size="2">~ Nuggets of Justice Message Board ~</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=3814"><font face="tempus sans itc" color="#0024FF" size="2">Level 52 Vicar</font></a></td><td align="center"><a href="http://pub30.ezboard.com/fnuggetsofjusticefrm3.showMessage?topicID=14.topic"><font color="#00F824" face="tempus sans itc" size="2">Want List</font></a>  </td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujbwithers.showPublicProfile?language=EN>JBWithers</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://wwp.icq.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=14332928&img=5 BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Singing cleric</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font colo